<section id="about">
    <div class="Why">
        <div class="row text-center" id="heading">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 wow animated zoomInDown" id="heading-text">
                <h3 style="font-size: 44px; color: #36ab9f;
                
                line-height: 50px;">Why Technically Black?</h3>
                <p> Creating a New Tomorrow</p>
                <hr style="border-top: 2px solid goldenrod;" class="full">
                <br/>
            </div>
        </div>	<!-- row -->
        <div class="row about-us-text">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
                <p class="text-center">I dedicate this Blog to the Black Tech ecosystem and underespresented groups in Technology.
                 I also dedicate this space to the future of Technology. May it be an inclusive space for all people.
                  As I was navigigating my career transition from teaching to technology, I searched for narratives similar to mine 
                  to connect with and to learn all the possibilites that lie ahead. As I searched, I found a plethora of great resources.
                 However, I did not find as many blogs and youtube videos from persons who look like me. 
                 I hope this can be another space full of resources for individuals like myself who aspire to transition. 
                A space for those who identify as Technically...Black.  </p>
            </div>
        </div>	<!-- row -->
    </section>
    <br><hr style="vertical-align: bottom; border: 2px dashed goldenrod;">

        

